Package com.opengamma.strata.basics.index

Interface IndexObservation

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    FxIndexObservation, IborIndexObservation, OvernightIndexObservation, PriceIndexObservation
    public interface IndexObservation
    A single observation of an index.

    Implementations of this interface represent observations of an index. For example, an observation of 'GBP-LIBOR-3M' at a specific fixing date.
